    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We have a requirement, if reseting 25 times in application, mcu should jump into bootloader."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "In order to troubleshoot whether it was caused by FUSA, We should print fusa error memory infomation to help analysis."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Solution"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "we can print the data of FUSA SM15 stored in retention RAM in the app in the bootloader."
    },
